Privacy Policy:
At CherrySoft Limited, Ireland, we are committed to protecting your privacy and ensuring the security of your personal information. This Privacy Policy outlines how we handle data collection and usage when you use our mobile applications.
1. Information Collection:
We do not collect or store any personal information about your use of our apps. We do not track your usage patterns, location, or any other data that could identify you as an individual user. Our applications are designed to operate independently on your device, and they do not communicate with our servers.
2. Crash Reporting:
To improve the functionality and performance of our apps, we utilize Google Crashlytics services to gather debug information in case of application crashes. This information is solely used for the purpose of identifying and resolving technical issues to enhance the user experience. Crashlytics may collect data such as device model, operating system version, and crash logs, but it does not gather personally identifiable information.
3. Third-Party Services:
Our apps may integrate with third-party services or include third-party libraries. Please note that these services or libraries may have their own privacy policies, and we encourage you to review them when using those features. We are not responsible for the privacy practices or content of these third-party services.
4. Data Security:
We take appropriate measures to ensure the security of your personal information. This includes implementing industry-standard safeguards to protect against unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction of data. Please note that as mentioned earlier, we do not collect any personal information from our users.
5. Childrenâ€™s Privacy:
Our apps are intended for users of age 8 and above. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under the age of 8. If we discover that we have inadvertently collected data from a child under 8, we will promptly delete it from our systems.
6. Changes to the Privacy Policy:
We reserve the right to update or modify this Privacy Policy at any time. Any changes will be reflected on this page, and we encourage you to review this policy periodically.
By using our apps, you signify your acceptance of this Privacy Policy. If you have any questions or concerns regarding our privacy practices, please contact us at [Contact Information].
